      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/25/3",
      "text": [
        ": قلت لأبي عبد الله: جعلت فداك، متى الفرج؟ فقال: يا أبا بصير، وأنت ممن يريد الدنيا؟ من عرف هذا الأمر فقد فرج عنه بانتظاره."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "3. Muhammad ibn Ya'qub narrated to us, from Ali ibn Muhammad, who reported it to Ali ibn Abi Hamza, from Abi Basir, who said: I said to Abu Abdullah, \"May I be sacrificed for you, when will the relief (al-Faraj) come?\" He replied, \"O Aba Basir, are you among those who desire this world? Whoever understands this matter has already found relief by awaiting it.\""
        ]
      }
    },
